{{USEflag|package=media-sound/audacious}}

{{USEflag|package=media-plugins/audacious-plugins}}

=== Emerge ===

Install {{Package|media-sound/audacious}} and {{Package|media-plugins/audacious-plugins}}:

{{emerge|media-sound/audacious media-plugins/audacious-plugins}}

== Usage ==

* To put Audacious in classic Winamp mode, go to ''View > Interface > Winamp Classic Interface''.

* To insert classical Winamp EQ presets:

{{Cmd|wget -O $HOME/.config/audacious/eq.preset https://gist.github.com/666threesixes666/6017524/raw/6f92831829453dd659f063299ba1bdf775a893ac/wapresets}}

